Correction, the device is a HTC MDA Vario III.

@fotoman21:

try this:

-> start - settings - external gps 
-> set the GPS port to com 0
-> set gps hardware port to none (off)
-> set gps to manage automatically

Then configure your application to the same settings. Worked for me with google maps, i'll update when i get this download!
